messages.message: Single Field (which will be renamed to Text) is the data type that all fields are by default. im not sure what a better ui would be here
yeah, lets think about it. I do not have an immediate other suggestion. It just looks weird right now. Maybe if you already know it is a table, or if we know it is an excel, we can change the default
Especially if you upload an excel, this is nearly never what you'd expect to be looking for

btw i think there are known limitations for our table detection logic during digitization for excel files

cc @Prashant Kikani

> When I corrected the field to "Table", it worked fine (which by the way is an enormous improvement!!).
We only use TDF(tabular data framework) when "Table" field is enabled, otherwise we use an older Weaviate based pipeline to extract fields. So, this kind of makes sense because older pipeline uses the PDF of an Excel.
